                <p>A few months ago, she decided to learn coding full-time and started to study Ruby, JavaScript, Node, Angular and React. Her <a href="https://github.com/mfhan?tab=repositories">GitHub page</a> is modest but shows that she wants to build real working apps and pages.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Members Section -->
    <section id="members" class="content-section text-center">
        <div class="members-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
                    <h2>Other Members</h2>
                    <p>Here are the other members of this groups</p>
                    <a href="../members" class="btn btn-default btn-lg">Visit Members Page</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
